1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:12,530
♪Longing during the day
and loneliness at night♪

2
00:00:12,830 --> 00:00:19,700
♪Clouds drift and curl,
and the cold rain falls again♪

3
00:00:20,460 --> 00:00:26,100
♪Green grass once dreamed of the world
and enlightened me♪

4
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:32,990
♪I crossed the sea of suffering
but couldn't escape your gaze♪

5
00:00:33,190 --> 00:00:39,930
♪Look at the bright moon
across the Milky Way♪

6
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:46,990
♪All love poems will record our story
from now on♪

7
00:00:47,060 --> 00:00:53,700
♪The thought of the distant mountain
makes my heart ache for my hometown♪

8
00:00:53,840 --> 00:01:01,520
♪Stone of Three Lifetimes reflects fate.
You once rode past on horseback♪

9
00:01:02,020 --> 00:01:03,640
=Just Wanna Be With You=

10
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:05,360
(Adapted From
Zhihu Novelist, Little Qi's)

11
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:07,260
("Three Marriages
to the Underworld Lord")

12
00:01:07,260 --> 00:01:10,260
=Episode 2=

13
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:13,640
You two are usually inseparable,

14
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:16,680
but I didn't see her today.

15
00:01:26,319 --> 00:01:27,040
How dare you?

16
00:01:27,079 --> 00:01:28,120
How dare you hit me?

17
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:30,040
Who allowed you to touch me?

18
00:01:30,359 --> 00:01:32,280
As the mistress of Cangyun,
I now order you

19
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,879
to leave my room. Go!

20
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:40,239
Yes.

21
00:01:41,799 --> 00:01:42,640
Your Excellency.

22
00:01:53,959 --> 00:01:55,799
(No, I must find Yu.)

23
00:01:59,260 --> 00:02:01,460
(Foxfolk)

24
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:13,879
Jiu.

25
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:16,199
Why did you

26
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:18,560
repeatedly break into Cangyun for me?

27
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,199
Because I can't forget you.

28
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,759
I can't forget
every day we spent together.

29
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:34,599
(Galloping on a horse in the drizzle
and falling apricot blossom,)

30
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:36,199
(I will never forget)

31
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,560
(the days I spent with you.)

32
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:39,800
(I'm from a humble background)

33
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:41,280
(and look up to celestial clan.)

34
00:02:42,439 --> 00:02:43,520
(You appeared in my life)

35
00:02:44,439 --> 00:02:45,960
(like a light.)

36
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:48,760
Do you want to give it a try?

37
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,479
Lingxiao clan ruled

38
00:02:50,599 --> 00:02:52,560
that Goddess can't drink alcohol.

39
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,680
Who cares about the stupid rules?

40
00:02:55,039 --> 00:02:56,000
Drink if you want.

41
00:02:58,319 --> 00:02:59,360
Here, take it.

42
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:02,680
Try it.

43
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:22,599
(You taught me how to drink.)

44
00:03:23,719 --> 00:03:25,159
(Let me teach you a poem.)

45
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:28,719
May your heart mirror mine.

46
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:33,000
I will never let you down.

47
00:03:43,479 --> 00:03:44,240
Alright.

48
00:03:44,639 --> 00:03:45,759
Go further

49
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:48,080
and you will reach foxfolk territory.

50
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:54,759
Time flies.

51
00:03:54,919 --> 00:03:56,520
Goddess Jiang Zhiyu.

52
00:03:58,319 --> 00:03:59,080
Really?

53
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:03,639
I also think time flies.

54
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:06,759
I'm going to go.

55
00:04:14,778 --> 00:04:18,858
♪Wild geese glide past
the autumn in my eyes♪

56
00:04:19,534 --> 00:04:22,850
♪Spring has gone and never returned♪

57
00:04:24,436 --> 00:04:28,472
♪The low moon weighs down my weary brow♪

58
00:04:28,509 --> 00:04:32,370
♪I drink alone
with no one to share the night♪

59
00:04:34,130 --> 00:04:37,883
♪The setting sun shatters my thoughts♪

60
00:04:37,992 --> 00:04:38,792
How beautiful.

61
00:04:38,792 --> 00:04:42,640
♪Like snow falling across the sky♪

62
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:46,959
How beautiful.

63
00:04:51,399 --> 00:04:52,160
Do you like it?

64
00:04:54,959 --> 00:04:56,519
I'll catch you a few.

65
00:04:57,185 --> 00:05:01,890
♪Even more I fear the long road
with no one beside me♪

66
00:05:02,334 --> 00:05:06,938
♪Chasing moon and breeze,
I drink to longing♪

67
00:05:06,938 --> 00:05:11,425
♪Grew old in silence,
never said what I meant♪

68
00:05:11,650 --> 00:05:16,123
♪I fear time turning to ash in a blink♪

69
00:05:16,392 --> 00:05:21,178
♪Even more I fear my thoughts
drifting under sky and sea♪

70
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:25,927
♪One journey through life
brings sorrow more than joy♪

71
00:05:26,043 --> 00:05:30,901
♪Tell me what love in this world
comes without tears♪

72
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,040
Here.

73
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:39,720
Look.

74
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,600
How beautiful.

75
00:05:57,745 --> 00:06:01,469
♪Like snow falling across the sky♪

76
00:06:02,760 --> 00:06:03,800
They're called fireflies.

77
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,000
Don't you have them in Cangyun?

78
00:06:05,079 --> 00:06:05,879
No.

79
00:06:06,079 --> 00:06:08,040
I've never seen this in Cangyun.

80
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,600
They're like small lanterns.

81
00:06:11,672 --> 00:06:16,058
♪I fear time turning to ash in a blink♪

82
00:06:16,516 --> 00:06:21,200
♪Even more I fear the long road
with no one beside me♪

83
00:06:21,534 --> 00:06:23,498
♪Chasing moon and breeze,♪

84
00:06:23,839 --> 00:06:25,680
They're beautiful.

85
00:06:29,279 --> 00:06:31,560
(I'll catch all the fireflies
and give them to you.)

86
00:06:32,319 --> 00:06:33,560
(They'll light up the night sky)

87
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,360
(like stars.)

88
00:06:35,839 --> 00:06:36,399
(Follow me.)

89
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,199
Jiang Zhiyu.

90
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:41,160
I like you.

91
00:06:43,160 --> 00:06:45,243
♪Brings sorrow more than joy♪

92
00:06:45,260 --> 00:06:50,363
♪Tell me what love in this world
comes without tears♪

93
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:55,120
Yu.

94
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:59,120
Yu.

95
00:07:05,759 --> 00:07:06,399
Help!

96
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:09,800
Help!

97
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,439
Help!

98
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:27,720
(Master?)

99
00:07:29,279 --> 00:07:30,759
(Why are you here?)

100
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:54,519
Here.

101
00:07:55,279 --> 00:07:55,920
Come with me.

102
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:14,320
We foxfolk

103
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:16,360
only wear flowers for the girl we love.

104
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:19,880
Wear flowers in this life and you'll be
beautiful in the next life.

105
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:22,440
I'm willing to wear flowers
for you forever.

106
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:23,080
Are you willing?

107
00:08:25,199 --> 00:08:25,800
I...

108
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,080
Where are you from?

109
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:43,840
Is it you?

110
00:08:44,639 --> 00:08:45,879
What do you mean?

111
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,480
You got the wrong person.

112
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:52,240
You haven't answered my question.

113
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,440
Sorry, Miss.

114
00:08:53,879 --> 00:08:54,480
I'm Yan Luo.

115
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:57,440
I accidentally entered Wanfu Forest
and encountered a ferocious beast today.

116
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:58,960
Luckily, you helped me.

117
00:08:59,519 --> 00:09:01,080
I wonder what's your name.

118
00:09:01,799 --> 00:09:02,720
It's fated.

119
00:09:03,039 --> 00:09:04,879
I also have Luo in my name.
My name is Luo Ying.

120
00:09:05,870 --> 00:09:11,350
♪It is not about running away♪

121
00:09:13,190 --> 00:09:19,550
♪I search for you across the vast sky,
but where are you now?♪

122
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,480
I'm not that powerful yet.

123
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:26,039
I can't help you recover immediately.

124
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,600
If my sister were here,

125
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,039
you would recover immediately.

126
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,480
Your sister...

127
00:09:31,159 --> 00:09:33,039
Cangyun's Goddess, Jiang Zhiyu.

128
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:45,759
Your Excellency,
I knew something was off.

129
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:47,879
Goddess is secretly meeting the foxfolk.

130
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:48,960
Find her.

131
00:09:53,970 --> 00:09:59,790
♪Dark clouds cover the stars
without a trace of light♪

132
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:05,780
♪Waiting for the wind
to clear the grey away♪

133
00:10:08,040 --> 00:10:11,610
♪Sudden rain falls
and I get soaked alone♪

134
00:10:11,700 --> 00:10:15,410
♪Even larks know where they belong♪

135
00:10:15,750 --> 00:10:21,230
♪It is not about running away♪

136
00:10:23,070 --> 00:10:29,430
♪I search for you across the vast sky,
but where are you now?♪

137
00:10:30,300 --> 00:10:35,380
♪I become a wisp of wind,
wiping away the clouds' traces♪

138
00:10:37,230 --> 00:10:40,670
♪I long to disappear without a trace,
wrapped in mystery♪

139
00:10:40,780 --> 00:10:44,450
♪If I send your loneliness
back to the sky♪

140
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:50,200
♪It can only rest inside your dreams♪

141
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:55,300
♪You and I gaze
at the endless Milky Way♪

142
00:10:55,300 --> 00:10:57,430
♪Holding each other so near♪

143
00:10:57,660 --> 00:11:04,810
♪If I were granted
a pair of splendid wings♪

144
00:11:04,870 --> 00:11:09,880
♪I could chase memories
in place of the right to love♪

145
00:11:09,940 --> 00:11:12,530
♪But the Milky Way never ends♪

146
00:11:12,620 --> 00:11:19,330
♪In this thin robe,
I wait for your reply♪
